name: Morning mist
description:
Yin can turn into yang. And yang can be transformed into yin.
One thing is both yin and yang, depends on many things.

The mist is yin, the wind is yang.
The cold is yin, warmth is yang.
Blue is yin, yellow is yang.
Evening is yin, morning is yang.

This photo is one of the ''Yin and yang'' series.
